profile_positions.description:
This role is part of the Business Travel Global Partnerships team in Booking.com. The primary task of this role is to offer operational and commercial support to the global commercial team in onboarding, managing and maintaining the relationships with Booking.com Business travel new and existing partners. 

Tasks:
- Build a close relationship with our existing and new Business Travel partners as the first point of contact for all operational needs;
- Provide commercial and operational support to the Business Travel Partnerships team members worldwide;
- Create and implement standard oprational process in addition to improve the existing workflows;
- Support in finding solutions for escalated issues;
- Prepare workshops and trainings for the commercial team
- Assist in the preparation of business reviews;
- Lead several operational projects that help drive Business Travel partnerships performance;
- Liaise between the Global Business Travel team in HQ and the Regional Commercial Teams around the globe.

As a Senior Customer Service role I am a part of the 2nd line of support to the customers and partners of Booking.com and the 1st line of support to the Customer and partner service agents of Booking.com.

Tasks:
- Respond to urgent and/or sensitive partner inbound via the different channels, and provide resolution in accordance with  Booking.com service standards;
- Manage urgent and/or sensitive guests inbound via the different channels, and provide resolution in accordance with  Booking.com service standards;
- Provide accurate, valid and complete information by using the right tools, methods and processes
- Handle predominantly routine cases but may require deviation from standard screens, procedures and ways of working
- Serves as an expert team member that will support CS Partner/guest Executive and CS Partner/guest Specialist colleagues with questions and help drive improvements
- Ensure a high level of partner/guests service and a positive partner experience, by giving a timely, efficient and professional support
- Meet service targets and call handling quotas;
- Support the analysis of data, supply feedback and recommend improvements.
